column5: HAPPY HOUR IN NEWFOUNDLAND...     A Newfie saw a sign at a restaurant. It  read....  ' Happy Hour Special' 'Lobster Tail & Beer'.   'Lard 'Tunderin' Jaises !' he says to himself, 'Me tree  favourite  tings'.
thats a good one joey Brian will like that for sure  rob
I don't get the joke..they are my 3 favourite things too           LOL
....I know Brian and he'll tell y'all that them thar is only 2 tings!
That was funny right there, Joanne.
